px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;美以与伊朗的战争引发了油价的大幅上涨。华盛顿的暴力言论和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/bvqY_FhjRD31DEuqmoq213yW14og9A4KRmwS4QuKveXJ3qv5UOBrFOhSWlSpzkjpCMf0OIzC0H79cXxl3E-AMyEMbkhjillqNx7o2aGu8_4bETXzTuhx9LHleZjUx-DRdnm4k05HzmtZxgGorJ2T1EqDGfF9ERYA5-HOhyVyoT2h_aTwDDlZcObyAtK0AFpiNZwhQpI8_1lEj4JMpw2N53RHnwCFaio6JSlrYdGR_fTUIX-BR0JSSxbrX1A0PgEZMDipA-VTuJy8S51M1RVoP8ArVeOUmDThLReeqlcdjUtbjExL0HnsSlCAIPQ6lFrOl6vTv0Bc2VNh3bzJzT0gq7drlkOQ_hRxBamAszbFF3XeEp0i9KQpN7FFmiMNaVm_ZAmfP5G2dnVMd0pWqJ0d0JFI5I9CxnxD_eWJjJQ0HWqzN99MnYWOBu9CAIafgoEX6jpRWnit2CzWYmmqsIr4jxk-eQqPhBE_5WPwJPulAuIRQGz4_Pkb18-cSho7Sy0GVMuLSdkM/w_HoASLkbOjOFD78ToSZAr2YsXDsGKIl/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗领导人通过好战言论和公开游行反抗特朗普"&gt;德黑兰威胁进行更广泛的报复，&lt;/a&gt;导致现场没有留下明显的出口。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/XacGvopmS_uwIzOqmBoGHyzi1UacOuLZqmOelTdDfOMrzd-V06SzD0oN_2kcrkRCtVX55DyzuI0LcuIQPu8pYYGiZf5yUl1cEocO3d5breI7GRpCwDJknm_vHa0r9GDVVddJIYk-pFUt_lImZFS9JWNYG9SFH2CRF3KpZ_EGC7ZFfChzVf48II29T-L2nTEi3z3kMgGtBYFjrR0aSWeTS0wqgqDUk5fMY_FI73xJOrKZoJ9mWkXIu4F6IvjdgcPnUB1O9tvYrrIoVddUiyoFzdUyenqaTWCndX982UEdm0QKDtMufzQKl0M75pJmMl0hriGH7OxKKc8mTPxzw2LXnSMy26HtzUhcA30LnHWuj0D8RfJGhWzhTgDjNuQeWqEMMKtjoKxfN1V1PdZdZxf9dzMqTOj1-coTfYJ_c11X8Ql03-6xupjsWWfHeJC4Wxiim2PRe6t2RnjUze3q60BqwjFwXvsuL9PwvJ7K8fLZF_MiQxHgS8N4MuFcKqsvrlGyK10Ufg/WCscTh4GuQMeJwsN3Xy3ZxQpzmoVuvfs/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着战争升温，股市下跌，布伦特原油价格突破 100 美元：市场结束"&gt;股市跳水&lt;/a&gt;和忧心忡忡的消费者正面临着美国乃至全世界失业和通胀的严峻影响。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;对于投资者来说， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/wpvnY9ypItRVm1TjzRU-1-41aWVLfB3na_6wU_v7qSyyPSoBBx5AgBgJnPqJTzxiXVC1mU9YjD4x-NFW1TyOUGHaBrzw4huR6X24XBkMEKj0qHx7evWz_LPY2FKmPviBfSCjNCwRS8APUih7TjMJ3QjAfz3PoCyKU4ZLVwH-Jxtd_eR1I8wTVrB0CLZhmf100TuVk1F_BziPha4LhtxMoGmxO1hbUUadU8BvEJKz1anC02Fp_rFaNC29W2t7H4Tda4jeuyJgc00REDML3IF