日益高涨&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;从在线银行和社交媒体到数字广告和人工智能订阅，数字服务是全球贸易中增长最快的部分。与实物出口不同，它们几乎不受监管、征税或关税。到目前为止。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;随着一条重要天然气管道的修复&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;，秘鲁多年来最严重的国内能源危机&lt;/strong&gt;即将结束。但在重大泄漏迫使该国主要天然气田&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Rb2ae4PuiGJBGLr4vtyg8xNKAGr3UDmBVp4FmnZpnvkSNniJxwLZi4AQvs61Hec3mnLJxM675-to351p75m6iptg5AUY9iw3Shkw_IItjy65jYIDH2SGEnKRVaAaCD08hLkGHeIWmJ7yk2FUXX1UhjssDhwazrCdAfv3mgpQfxRjnPIochTIeN1Ye8v14iDkBWS4CZj_yK1OuLl-_nUXK3SPJ2nePlZaltpfgXmmr6aktRcrz4T__8ODE-DWOhh4ETsNVTTx3cL2AfwjN-kAHCBUwlyZ1mcxXZRq6HrgLqXDiccdG5DRKGxcr6eNc4zTGUIBirhqkkaTJGXGdzYHUfmRvodEG6kXSSQNg28Ii4uiOOL2SMJ9hHkhURTjCeUZDSUR8QDRLuK6iUKwwgGsllag7JhjAdK-J2kTJc0mytPqhcOdwHovJFdzJ7T1lYWvnJaxJLzpthXSI7eZEbnkqUj6vMnczts7FdkO6lprfr_esloBDgE0MmAMXesL8Ed13Mt7BmM/ihmDSQGOO4WmNpEnFUTpwzY9zmDJzvIu/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着配给开始，天然气危机袭击秘鲁企业"&gt;停止运输燃料&lt;/a&gt;近两周后，这将导致通货膨胀暂时飙升。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;就在伊朗战争导致全球价格飙升之际，这场危机导致了燃料配给，并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/CM5otaZb_0Ln2tN7K-TZaJ1HSP78JNFKzxQhrT99ZcQXS9hXGTU7Y6yllkgmYH_q3xbYE6Y0o-HAwSBFABgTWxpQakdFkCrYQYVOo88ozEzEcsYy2Ccut60qrhCNFJWtigPXGdy8IYV2CSUeEo_E47yEk9tiOe8REpksWN7iB5ensdCW9U3bXjYgcnfzX2PHPEjyjZeuZ-vclCL206pEP6ItqNVZg2SoXQ6uRjPesKJo-QmKgbXu1JgO0mBvsTnq9U3x6CjXqRE0KatRzUjdRcfGCUeBWKgwAmDgjBjoPQvSDk4mrJoTF5YOgtJ-sLj_maS0V0rAGeKNqbmKFRuAhdx_nWqFJGBcWbWEykuU0j-oMijjDCh1O2ktN5iyjGG2_tMBudRBb_C5BoN4pGDyGz5Pa28Tz2-Jk4Ihcxbx9aanPIC1m